{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.1", "text_original": "節南山\n節彼南山，維石巖巖。赫赫師尹，民具爾瞻。\n憂心如惔，不敢戲談。國既卒斬，何用不監！", "text_normalized": "節南山\n節彼南山，維石巖巖。赫赫師尹，民具爾瞻。\n憂心如惔，不敢戲談。國既卒斬，何用不監！", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.2", "text_original": "節彼南山，有實其猗。赫赫師尹，不平謂何？\n天方薦瘥，喪亂弘多。民言無嘉，憯莫懲嗟。", "text_normalized": "節彼南山，有實其猗。赫赫師尹，不平謂何？\n天方薦瘥，喪亂弘多。民言無嘉，憯莫懲嗟。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.3", "text_original": "尹氏大師，維周之氐。秉國之均，四方是維。\n天子是毗，俾民不迷。不弔昊天，不宜空我師。", "text_normalized": "尹氏大師，維周之氐。秉國之均，四方是維。\n天子是毗，俾民不迷。不弔昊天，不宜空我師。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.4", "text_original": "弗躬弗親，庶民弗信；弗問弗仕，勿罔君子？\n式夷式已，無小人殆。瑣瑣姻亞，則無膴仕。", "text_normalized": "弗躬弗親，庶民弗信；弗問弗仕，勿罔君子？\n式夷式已，無小人殆。瑣瑣姻亞，則無膴仕。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.5", "text_original": "昊天不傭，降此鞠訩。昊天不惠，降此大戾。\n君子如屆，俾民心闋。君子如夷，惡怒是違。", "text_normalized": "昊天不傭，降此鞠訩。昊天不惠，降此大戾。\n君子如屆，俾民心闋。君子如夷，惡怒是違。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.6", "text_original": "不弔昊天，亂靡有定。式月斯生，俾民不寧。\n憂心如酲，誰秉國成？不自為政，卒勞百姓。", "text_normalized": "不弔昊天，亂靡有定。式月斯生，俾民不寧。\n憂心如酲，誰秉國成？不自為政，卒勞百姓。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 6."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__007__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.7", "text_original": "駕彼四牡，四牡項領。我瞻四方，蹙蹙靡所騁。", "text_normalized": "駕彼四牡，四牡項領。我瞻四方，蹙蹙靡所騁。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 7."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__008__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.8", "text_original": "方茂爾惡，相爾矛矣。既夷既懌，如相醻矣。", "text_normalized": "方茂爾惡，相爾矛矣。既夷既懌，如相醻矣。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 8."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__009__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.9", "text_original": "昊天不平，我王不寧。不懲其心，覆怨其正。", "text_normalized": "昊天不平，我王不寧。不懲其心，覆怨其正。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 9."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__010__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.10", "text_original": "家父作誦，以究王訩。式訛爾心，以畜萬邦。", "text_normalized": "家父作誦，以究王訩。式訛爾心，以畜萬邦。", "notes": "節南山 Chinese stanza 10."}
